### Phase 3: Authentication Strategy (Supabase Auth)
> [!NOTE]
> We will use a **Hybrid Authentication Model** to balance frictionless onboarding for owners and practical access for staff.

- **Business Owners (Primary Registration)**: 
    - **Method**: Google OAuth (SSO).
    - **Reason**: 1-click registration, high security, no password fatigue. Perfect for high-conversion onboarding on the main landing page (`bizzy.id`).
- **Staff / Employees (Kasir, Gudang)**:
    - **Method**: Username & Password / PIN.
    - **Reason**: Owner dapat dengan mudah men-generate akun generik (misal: Username: `kasir_cabang1`, PIN: `123456`) di Dashboard mereka tanpa perlu email sungguhan. Staff login langsung di subdomain `namatoko.bizzy.id`.
- **Technical Handling**: 
    - Supabase Auth akan dikonfigurasi untuk memungkinkan login tanpa email (menggunakan kombinasi Username/Unique Phone Number + Password).
    - Wildcard redirect URLs (`*.bizzy.id/auth/callback`) akan di-setting untuk SSO Owner.

